in pace setter state therefore encouraged the youth to love what they are doing and be determined to achieve their dreams passionately. Veteran broadcaster and the General manager of PETALS FM, Dotun Saseyi noted the contributions of past Nigerian heroes and urged the youth to be strategic and holistic in their dealing as success walk in line with hard work. The event which was held at Palms 77 Hotel and suites, Agodi Ibadan attracted a large number of youth across all walks of life. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION